data.description: Architecturally stunning custom one story home. From the moment you walk up to the front door you will be struck by the custom design and exacting attention to detail. The home offers an open floorplan with a beautiful chef's kitchen, solid wood cabinetry, and a full complement of stainless steel appliances. You will find architectural detailing throughout the home including crown molding, tray ceilings, and arched wood doors with wrought iron inserts. The oversized master includes a fireplace and a sumptuous bath with his and her accommodations. The spacious downstairs living area also includes tile and carpet floors, a second fireplace, & beautiful accents throughout. The exterior of the home is finished in brick with stone accents. The expansive front and back porches are elaborately detailed with arches, columns, wood ceilings and ceiling fan. Large corner lot is ideal for outdoor relaxation and entertaining. Oversized 3 car garage with guest apartment above it is an amazing bonus!
